<div class="help-section">
  <h1>Welcome to the Project Hub User Manual</h1>
  <p>
    This manual provides an overview of ProjectHub's features, focusing on how the Project Hub integrates 
    and streamlines your workflow. Whether you're new to the platform or need a refresher, this guide 
    will walk you through the essential functionalities step by step.
  </p>

  <% @document = Document.find_by(title: "Project Hub User Manual") %>

  <% if @document && @document.attachments.any? %>
    <div class="download-section">
      <p>
        To get a detailed understanding of the Project Hub, download the official 
        <strong>Project Hub User Manual</strong>. Click the button below:
      </p>
      <%= link_to 'Download User Manual', 
                  download_tra_user_module_path(@document.id), 
                  class: 'btn btn-primary icon icon-download' %>
    </div>
  <% else %>
    <div class="no-document-section">
      <p>
        The <strong>Project Hub User Manual</strong> is currently unavailable for download. Please 
        check back later or contact the support team if you need immediate assistance.
      </p>
    </div>
  <% end %>
</div>


